data.title: An Excellent New Mediterranean Restaurant
data.text:
I tried this restaurant on a whim because it looked interesting. My first afternoon back in Berkeley so I didn't know anything about it. I chose take out although there are tables. The king falafel wrap was superb. Prepared after I ordered. The waiter gave me a glass of tea while I waited. There was also mint infused water. I'd love to try some of the other items but won't be here long enough.
This is a new family owned restaurant.
